Alias      Myanti-Lambda_c(2593)-       anti-Lambda_c(2593)-
ChargeConj MyLambda_c(2593)+       Myanti-Lambda_c(2593)-
#
Alias       MyLambda_c+        Lambda_c+
Alias  Myanti-Lambda_c-        anti-Lambda_c-
