#
Alias  MyH_30     A0
Alias  Myanti-H_30    A0
ChargeConj MyH_30   Myanti-H_30
#
Decay B+sig
    1.000   MyLambda_c(2593)+   MyH_30    PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig
#
Decay MyLambda_c(2593)+
    1.000      MyLambda_c+ pi+ pi-             PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Lambda_c(2593)-
#
